# 📁 File Management System

A production-ready backend API for securely uploading, organizing, and managing files.

Built with **Node.js**, **Express.js**, **TypeScript**, **PostgreSQL**, and **Prisma**, this project follows modern backend engineering practices such as modular architecture, authentication, centralized error handling, logging, validation, testing, and cloud storage integration.

---

## 🚀 Features

- User Authentication (JWT)
- Secure File Upload
- Folder Management
- File Sharing
- Search & Pagination
- AWS S3 Storage
- Logging with Pino
- Request Validation
- Centralized Error Handling
- Production-ready Project Structure

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| Node.js | Runtime |
| Express.js | Web Framework |
| TypeScript | Language |
| PostgreSQL | Database |
| Prisma | ORM |
| Pino | Logging |
