Base URL

```
http://localhost:5000/api/v1
```

Current Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| GET | /health | Health Check |

---

## 🏗 Architecture

The project follows a modular architecture.

```
Controller
     │
Service
     │
Repository (Prisma)
     │
PostgreSQL
```

Each module contains its own:

- Controller
- Service
- Routes
- Validation
- Types

